{"tid":590823,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"勸世文 其實你係唔係成日打J 一睇就知","createTime":"2018-03-13T03:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T05:12:52.000Z","uid":192,"like":19,"dislike":209,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"a9664e8039657de720382a53cdc438bc22fb38d3","tid":590823,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"成日打Jer仔既人會好怕同異性有交流<br />\n因為當你望住個靚女 佢又望緊你既時候<br />\n班日日打Jer仔既毒撚個腦會無意地有咸濕既思想（姐係見到人著裙又望人隻腳 見到見衫有少少突就係到諗衰野個d)<br />\n所以成日打jer仔個d人通常面對女仔都會好小心咁交流 好似好怕比人識穿佢好撚咸濕成日打Jer仔<br />\n扮出黎個種自然其實真係好易睇得出<br />\n都係個句 打少d Jer啦<br />\n又唔係叫你完全唔好打 <br />\n但一日一J/兩日一J 支出多過收入咩都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面又有返血色 唔做運動但都唔會未至於跑400米都哮喘咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔差在貼埋另一個link啦<br />\n縱欲其實係慢慢咁破壞前途<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/375000/page/28?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/375000/page/28?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此PosT含0.03%ACG成份<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/114037_4480d1170fda1ba16eba57d1e03d1c3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F114037_4480d1170fda1ba16eba57d1e03d1c3f.png&h=7b566bd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6159cdd6219dd166324e48cb7e6ff74ddd8b5c8e","tid":590823,"uid":192,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"利申一日一J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537f5afcebc2c681d53983720992a7484fed9cb1","tid":590823,"uid":2223,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"駁&hellip;唔&hellip;到&hellip;"},{"pid":"e5a1ba2e1bec3e36c61dd65d1aeb433cab5a685c","tid":590823,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"537f5afcebc2c681d53983720992a7484fed9cb1","tid":590823,"uid"